window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Perry Z has a Magical Destiny.</p> <p>Born to a Magical Fantasy Princess and a nine-to-five Supervillain in the most superhero riddled city in the world, Perry's never felt...adequate. He's got no talent for magic, and not a scrap of superpowers to his name.</p> <p>When The System boots and unlocks his powers, it forces him to follow in his father's footsteps, but he'd rather take after his mother...</p> <p>Maybe there's a way he can do both...</p>"; 
